Setup instructions:
**********************************

Special gem requirements:
============================
uuidtools > 2.0.0
ZenTest > 4.1

Other gem requirements: 
============================
(I am not certain that all of these are actually required, the list was taken
from the deployment.log file)

Linguistics
RedCloth
babel
builder
cached_model
capistrano
capistrano-ext
facets
fastercsv
hoe
hpricot
json
json_pure
log4r
memcache-client
mocha
money
mongrel
mongrel_cluster
rcov
rmagick
rspec
tzinfo
uuidtools
validatable
webgen
xmpp4r

Other important notes:
=========================

The test suite will not run correctly without first running:

  rake sage:makemo
